data.description: This is your chance to become the proud owner of this lovely completely remodeled move-in ready residence nestled in the 55+ Sun Air Estates Community! New roof, A/C, New Windows, Ceiling fans throughout, No popcorn ceilings with over 30K spent on renovations. Explore inside to discover a perfectly flowing layout showcasing gleaming wood-look floors throughout and designer color palette. The spotless eat-in kitchen boasts butcher block counters, stylish tile backsplash, brand-new stainless-steel appliances, and white cabinetry for ample storage. You will find generously sized bedrooms offering ceiling fans and closets for easy organization. Spend relaxing afternoons in the cozy covered patio, surrounded by trees and picturesque blue skies! Don't let this opportunity pass you by!
